{"tid":143094,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"鋸木條應該用咩嚟鋸","createTime":"2017-03-04T10:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T11:58:41.000Z","uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f41b0ca2835efea505a4415d13bfd5f4aaccdb7","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:41:58.000Z","msg":"飛機木嚟，想係屋企都鋸到，打直鋸兩條1cm<br />\n條木太窄，屋企又冇嘢夾實條木<br />\n今日唔知頭唔知路去買咗把鋸木板嘅鋸，鋸咗成個字先鋸得幾cm，仲要鋸得唔順暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89AiUAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89AiUAX.png&h=a008e09a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知用下面呢隻可唔可以唔洗夾實條木而又鋸得快<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://www.cabinhouse8.com/upload/product/HandTools/50999-1.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cabinhouse8.com%2Fupload%2Fproduct%2FHandTools%2F50999-1.jpg&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ee251919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cabinhouse8.com/upload/product/HandTools/50999-1.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]"},{"pid":"98b4f6fe7bfd120bcb6db6d64df6562fdca1031e","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:42:55.000Z","msg":"下面哩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d664sv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd664sv2.jpg&h=5ddbfda6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9658d2f350a669c665d7494ec0d43354c63d8cc","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828c54e4c874cce5126cd6a37262f22f873c4411","tid":143094,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:13:05.000Z","msg":"用倉頡輸入法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6a1b41f4f61bb6fc2cf5b41fb8d26ddc11b5cb","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e838a89e718e440a4cb6dbd132ec26f1d41c0e8a","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用倉頡輸入法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6deb24b228e964d2966aa574953bb453f92e1c","tid":143094,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:16:01.000Z","msg":"買過條叫人鋸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d3c4c6b8f81effc7386dd5fee835b4feed840b","tid":143094,"uid":15471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"飛機木就咁啪咪得"},{"pid":"2a43719e14cf94b5550791ac8e891d5c9ce9500b","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買過條叫人鋸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定要用嗰條，隻size冇師傅肯鋸<br />\n同埋係用嚟做lab<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04c13b32bfaf855f1feeafc15bea91c5959f2d9","tid":143094,"uid":56497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下面哩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d664sv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd664sv2.jpg&h=5ddbfda6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你果把係線鋸黎 鋸曲線用 你用佢都得但係應該鋸唔得直同慢<br />\n鋸木用板鋸夠曬 鋸得慢好有可能係你唔識用力同揸得唔夠直 試下每次行程大啲 每次都比啲力向下壓住拉/推（睇鋸齒方向）同埋唔好扭住把鋸就的"},{"pid":"82c2d0a7b6e36178d48e727c4fe1c00d2a58bbc6","tid":143094,"uid":8848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"去鋸木d鋪頭 問佢地扲個鋸床黎鋸 最多比返錢"},{"pid":"1fd76ea61c7605778e64fd1392a94f030194c25e","tid":143094,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"成條幾長?<br />\n0.5CM 是但五金鋪買把鋸都得啦, 藍色果隻鋸片"},{"pid":"75b189492b07f1ef382fccbffead832f5ba36193","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下面哩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d664sv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd664sv2.jpg&h=5ddbfda6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你果把係線鋸黎 鋸曲線用 你用佢都得但係應該鋸唔得直同慢<br />\n鋸木用板鋸夠曬 鋸得慢好有可能係你唔識用力同揸得唔夠直 試下每次行程大啲 每次都比啲力向下壓住拉/推（睇鋸齒方向）同埋唔好扭住把鋸就的</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我咁樣鋸，推落去都有少少卡住，一拉上嚟就完全唔流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5D21h6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5D21h6.png&h=d81cae99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n把鋸：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TtcWf81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTtcWf81.jpg&h=1f6ad50d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z9575fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9575fc.jpg&h=52724b98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea916a4e4d221188e9e41663d59cbb47849833d2","tid":143094,"uid":56497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:29:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下面哩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d664sv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd664sv2.jpg&h=5ddbfda6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你果把係線鋸黎 鋸曲線用 你用佢都得但係應該鋸唔得直同慢<br />\n鋸木用板鋸夠曬 鋸得慢好有可能係你唔識用力同揸得唔夠直 試下每次行程大啲 每次都比啲力向下壓住拉/推（睇鋸齒方向）同埋唔好扭住把鋸就的</blockquote><br />\n唔記得講 你鋸咁幼好考功夫 仲要咁薄 有可能比你出力鋸果陣推/拉爆成件工件 仲要未計鋸嘅時候會有損耗同誤差<br />\n你買兩件2cm嘅件鋸+磨都變1cm比較可行（買幾多張粗幼沙紙睇你實驗要幾準啦）"},{"pid":"193fb7dac45e595f27c530b08cba104737102096","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去鋸木d鋪頭 問佢地扲個鋸床黎鋸 最多比返錢</blockquote><br />\n聽日會去問下，最怕啲師傅話太幼唔肯鋸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企冇工具真係好難鋸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2757c04af459749a264d19219e6a1cf4df12a9ac","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成條幾長?<br />\n0.5CM 是但五金鋪買把鋸都得啦, 藍色果隻鋸片</blockquote><br />\n40cm*2cm*0.5cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b0cd4b4096a456ad614e18d801a67f0076bd40","tid":143094,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"徒手就得<br />\n樓豬去學學空手道先"},{"pid":"488d1f1b16b73a719aa1cb549e901abb57402baa","tid":143094,"uid":43,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/04/193621_8f530bb1a41292e62b7ba53691ed3d08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F04%2F193621_8f530bb1a41292e62b7ba53691ed3d08.jpg&h=40b25372&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1af49321f8cbf0c3bd725d8811d849b77bbcfcb6","tid":143094,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"淘寶買木工工具<br />\n有d無咁重型"},{"pid":"194f15474b9530ffb3c1707dbafeeb292c9dd62e","tid":143094,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成條幾長?<br />\n0.5CM 是但五金鋪買把鋸都得啦, 藍色果隻鋸片</blockquote><br />\n40cm*2cm*0.5cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/YKQp8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FYKQp8&h=77a9b6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搵張椅(藍色)墊住, 申少少木出黎, 左右兩邊叫你老母搵鉗仔鉗住, 跟住你中間鋸<br />\n唔順就水平D 鋸"},{"pid":"b281ce3c6af192af6412b74f923353415f17f093","tid":143094,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2KkpDxK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2KkpDxK.jpg&h=8ce76c62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8b2c252d9ca4d852ee6671ae9e2917584aabaff","tid":143094,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"你隻鋸片咁粗劏牛咩, 去五金鋪買藍色果隻啦, D 牙幼好多"},{"pid":"6dbaf7827d4ffce313965e9d1057faa14618d1bb","tid":143094,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://shop.cpu.com.tw/upload/2010/06/org/9cdf1106ffd3dee37ee32fda2d5c6d4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshop.cpu.com.tw%2Fupload%2F2010%2F06%2Forg%2F9cdf1106ffd3dee37ee32fda2d5c6d4a.jpg&h=d0be8722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用呢隻鋸片是常識吧"},{"pid":"a905ac0013761b085ff1d39bfe5180b2b7572614","tid":143094,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://shop.cpu.com.tw/upload/2010/06/org/9cdf1106ffd3dee37ee32fda2d5c6d4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshop.cpu.com.tw%2Fupload%2F2010%2F06%2Forg%2F9cdf1106ffd3dee37ee32fda2d5c6d4a.jpg&h=d0be8722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用呢隻鋸片是常識吧</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86eb250f88bf1f90a85a64e3a5f035a459cacadc","tid":143094,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成條幾長?<br />\n0.5CM 是但五金鋪買把鋸都得啦, 藍色果隻鋸片</blockquote><br />\n40cm*2cm*0.5cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用界刀界幾下一啪就斷啦"}]}